On the upside, I agree with lots of these thoughts!

There's <a href="https://openhatch.org/bugs/issue246">https://openhatch.org/bugs/issue246</a> about making the page more 
*useful*. I just want to make sure users aren't led down the garden path 
into a part of the site that won't help them get involved in open source.</pre>
