   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Well, it does take a while to load but it's nice to see how many projects are in 
there. Maybe instead of ditching it, could just show the most popular (?) ones and 
then offer the search from there. 

Some ideas of "most popular" is to feature some by hand, or show those with the most 
bugs, or most contributors, or newest bugs.

Also, maybe an action button to lead those in that don't see their projects there. 
"Don't see your project? Add it here." (or something)</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
  <tr>
   <th><a href="msg1761">msg1761 (view)</a></th>
