  <tr>
   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>I just talked with someone who used the site and ending up on /+projects/.

I just thought about it, and I realized: that page is just useless. Let's ditch
it until we come up with a good way to have a projects page.

Any objections?

I know it just got a really nice-looking top drawing from aldeka but the page
wastes users' time. I want to ditch it until we figure out come up with a more
useful way to present projects to users.

(Really, we could have a neat tag-based project browser kinda like /search/ ?
But some other day.)</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
